    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about the risks, but honestly i've been reading a lot of stuff online about how some people manage their thinness just with super high doses of garlic and certain herbs. like, if i were to really go all out on the garlic extract, could that actually work as a way to stay thin without the warfarin? i'm just trying to see if there's a real alternative out there so i don't have to deal with all these medical appointments every week.",
